data.description: Beautiful Home with a well thought out floorpan & a two car garage plus toy garage for your mower/SXS/Golf Cart (whichever suites your needs).  Also, Cherokee Park Boat Launch is right around the corner approximately 1 mile away. Granite Countertops with custom cabinets, extra pantry space in the utility room, Primary Suite offers a bonus sitting room that can be used as a dressing room, powder room, extra closet, office space, etc. Wood Burning Pellet Stove in living room, real hardwoods floors throughout the home with tiled bathrooms, sunroom (currently used as office space) located off of the living room, covered back patio & partially fenced backyard. Guest Bedroom's closet was also built as a Safe Room. Tankless Water Heater for endless hot water. This home has been well kept & located in a family friendly neighborhood. Owners live there full time so please schedule appointment in advance & it's a must see!
